location.fullValue: Madrid Plan, Inspirada at Prairie Center Village

data.description: Located in the quiet, coveted Prairie Village Center in Brighton, this 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath property built in 2020 is the perfect home starter home!!! Within a half mile of the property, you can access groceries, shopping, restaurants, and Barr Lake State Park. Proximity to I-76 gives you access to the Denver Metro Area without paying the Metro Area prices for a similar square footage house. Add additional living space by finishing the 996-square-foot unfinished basement. This is an ideal space to add at least one extra bedroom and bathroom -  the rough-in plumbing is already installed. Call to schedule your showing now!
